{"tid":1861203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭口中嘅「專家顧問團」係邊幾個？","createTime":"2020-02-04T04:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T05:13:17.000Z","uid":78047,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8524244d908a8efb047a9b473753bcacd46f0c","tid":1861203,"uid":78047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:38:05.000Z","msg":"【#最新抗疫邏輯題：Condom召喚】<br />\n<br />\n1. 林鄭月娥在早前記者招待會，不斷強調特區「政府」一切「抗疫」「措施」，都是經「專家顧問團」同意。<br />\n<br />\n2. 林鄭月娥最新宣佈，戴口罩需要符合三大準則：自己病、上前線、去人多密集地方，否則「戴咗都要除返」。<br />\n<br />\n3. 香港已出現首宗武漢肺炎死亡個案，死者是39歲本地人；此外，衛生署也已證實出現本地人傳人個案，另有確診者情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4.「專家顧問團」只有4位成員，一律德高望重，包括梁卓偉教授 、福田敬義教授、袁國勇教授、許樹昌教授。請問邊位贊成林鄭月娥上述建議？</span><br />\n<br />\n「專家顧問團」再唔割蓆，一生清譽從此毀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/3021516637882466/?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F3021516637882466%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=d0429a41\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/3021516637882466/?sfnsn=mo</a>"},{"pid":"f146bf28234576b035b9b097b6a1d6a30d8cfad3","tid":1861203,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"Who 果條黑鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69f8d9bbef40c0a8ce1688a6654961b3f22273a","tid":1861203,"uid":78047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f146bf28234576b035b9b097b6a1d6a30d8cfad3","tid":1861203,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"Who 果條黑鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:40:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Funited